cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.SY, cs.COM 

The paper discusses the use of millimeter-wave frequencies in future mobile networks, which falls under the category of wireless communication and networking. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely sub-categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.COM (Computers and Society).
